    {
      "risk": "Training-serving skew despite Feature Store",
      "severity": "high",
      "mitigation": "Enforce that feature computation code is a shared library imported by both training and serving. Add integration tests that compute features for a fixed input in both paths and assert equality. Monitor prediction distribution drift in production."
    },
    {
      "risk": "100ms P99 latency budget exceeded under load",
      "severity": "critical",
      "mitigation": "Budget breakdown: feature lookup ~5ms (local cache + Redis), model inference ~5-10ms (LightGBM in-process), network overhead ~10-20ms, leaves 65ms headroom. Load test early. If weather API is external, cache aggressively (weather doesn't change per-request). NEVER make a synchronous external call in the serving path."
