      "mitigation": "Start simple. V1 Feature Store = shared Python module + Redis. V1 Model Registry = S3 bucket + single Postgres table. V1 Monitoring = Prometheus + Grafana. No Kubernetes, no Kubeflow, no MLflow until proven necessary. Each engineer owns one vertical slice."
