    {
      "risk": "Rollback gap — new model promoted, degrades, team doesn't notice for hours",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "Promote new models only during business hours. Post-promotion monitoring runbook: watch error dashboard for 30 minutes. Rollback is a single CLI command that re-labels the previous version as champion and restarts the inference service (or sends SIGHUP)."
