  "implementation_guidance": {
    "recommended_approach": "Phase 1 (Weeks 1-3): Build the inference service with a hand-tuned baseline model (e.g., distance/speed lookup table) to establish the serving path, latency baseline, and prediction logging. Phase 2 (Weeks 3-5): Build the Feature Store as a shared Python package, train the first ML model (LightGBM), wire up the Model Registry (S3 + Postgres). Phase 3 (Weeks 5-7): Build the training pipeline as a weekly Airflow/Prefect DAG, implement the Validation Gate, close the feedback loop. Phase 4 (Weeks 7-8): Monitoring, alerting, rollback runbook, load testing, shadow mode comparison against the baseline.",
