      "Data volume for training — if delivery history is small (<10K records), model quality may be limited regardless of architecture"
    ],
    "assumptions": [
      "Traffic volume is moderate (hundreds to low thousands QPS) — typical for a checkout flow",
      "Tabular features with ~6 inputs — LightGBM/XGBoost will outperform or match neural nets",
      "Weather data can be cached with 15-30 minute TTL without meaningful accuracy loss",
